The first set of Champions League fixtures after the international break, will be played this midweek across Europe. Club Brugge host Paris Saint-Germain, while Real Madrid travel to Galatasaray on Tuesday. Manchester City clash with Atalanta at the Etihad and Juventus welcome Lokomotiv Moscow. Bayern Munich are away at Olympiacos, while Atletico Madrid take on Bayer Leverkusen. Tuesday, October 22 GROUP A
